casebody.data:
Friday, April 30, 1993

MOTION DOCKET

90-1868. State v. Combs.

Hamilton County, No. C-880156. UPON CONSIDERATION of the motion filed by counsel for appellant to continue stay of execution scheduled to expire on April 26, 1993,

IT IS ORDERED by the court, effective April 27, 1993, that said motion be, and the same is hereby, granted, and said stay of execution is continued to May 10, 1993.
